(7, 9, 'Cricket', 6, 3, 'saikat', 'saikat@gmail.com', 6, 'Sports', 'Football vs Cricket', 'If you are a football fan, read it to get a bite of reality. If you are a cricket fan, read it to be proud on cricket.', '&lt;p&gt;Some people cheer for cricket and some for football.But both are best all over the world.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;I was naturally a cricket player.From childhood till the age of 13 I used to play cricket and thought that it was the best.But at the age of 13 I started playing football&amp;nbsp;. I was on a real football turf for the first time since my childhood. It was very difficult to excel in football.But slowly I found the difference s that took place.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://miro.medium.com/max/271/1*7-YEo4CS4svS8_Q7PnIZXQ.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;i&gt;There are lots of differences between football and cricket&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Cricket&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cricket is famous mostly in Asia&amp;nbsp;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;But all the countries play cricket.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cricket is a game where we need to have our eyes sights to be perfect.physical fitness doesnâ€™t matter that much.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cricket needs flexibility of our body so that we could excel in fielding&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Fielding&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Itâ€™s the most important thing that should be perfect in cricket&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Batsmen scores well in a match or gets out early in another match.Bowler takes 0â€“2 (average) in a match but a fielder has to take catches in all matches&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;So you can understand the importance of fielding.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Catches win matches&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Batting&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;It is just a matter of 1 ball&amp;nbsp;.1 ball, if you get out you will have to wait for another match to play&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Batting need practice and technique&amp;nbsp;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use of wrist is essential for batting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Bowling&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;It is the use of arm to throw a ball at a speed 140 kmph to get a batsman out.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Football&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;This game needs physical fitness at its best.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Football has many essential things such as passes, shots&amp;nbsp;,skills and touches&amp;nbsp;.Goal is the most important which decides the match winners&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Passes&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Passes it include soft touches to pass a ball from one player to another to attack for a goal.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Passes are of two types&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Long passes&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Short passes&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Long passes&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The players pass the ball from one player to another through aerial route.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Short passes&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The players pass the ball from one player to another when they are nearby.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Skills&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;These are tricks used by strickers to dominate the game&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://miro.medium.com/max/300/1*YpmcHDZCyiNttoTcoGv8Nw.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;Most of the strickers use skills such as step over and body feint and many others.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Shots&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;These are a type in f long passes which is aimed on goal at with lotâ€™s of power to score a goal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Goal&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The most important thing in football&amp;nbsp;.Goal decides the winner of football match.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Results&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Both are the best and have their own importance.so never compare the both games&lt;/p&gt;', '2019-08-23 03:05:17', '2019-08-23 03:05:17'),
(8, 10, 'Footbal', 6, 3, 'saikat', 'saikat@gmail.com', 6, 'Sports', 'Football vs Cricket', 'If you are a football fan, read it to get a bite of reality. If you are a cricket fan, read it to be proud on cricket.', '&lt;p&gt;Some people cheer for cricket and some for football.But both are best all over the world.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;I was naturally a cricket player.From childhood till the age of 13 I used to play cricket and thought that it was the best.But at the age of 13 I started playing football&amp;nbsp;. I was on a real football turf for the first time since my childhood. It was very difficult to excel in football.But slowly I found the difference s that took place.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://miro.medium.com/max/271/1*7-YEo4CS4svS8_Q7PnIZXQ.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;i&gt;There are lots of differences between football and cricket&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Cricket&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cricket is famous mostly in Asia&amp;nbsp;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;But all the countries play cricket.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cricket is a game where we need to have our eyes sights to be perfect.physical fitness doesnâ€™t matter that much.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cricket needs flexibility of our body so that we could excel in fielding&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Fielding&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Itâ€™s the most important thing that should be perfect in cricket&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Batsmen scores well in a match or gets out early in another match.Bowler takes 0â€“2 (average) in a match but a fielder has to take catches in all matches&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;So you can understand the importance of fielding.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Catches win matches&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Batting&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;It is just a matter of 1 ball&amp;nbsp;.1 ball, if you get out you will have to wait for another match to play&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Batting need practic